Instruction to build these benchmarks:
--------------------------------------
1) Install makefiles:
   1.1) checkout the makefiles from tcgl/trunk/make.
   1.2) make sure you have ROOT environment variable set.
   1.3) make install the makefiles.
2) Make sure that the following variables are set in your environment (these are example values):
   2.1) USE_SGAL=0
   2.2) PLATFORM=linux
   2.3) COMPILER_VER=4.0.4
   2.4) USE_GLUT=1
   2.5) USE_BOOST=1
   2.6) USE_CGAL=0
   2.7) USE_LEDA=0
   2.8) USE_QT=0
   2.9) USE_GMP=0
   2.10) USE_CORE=0

Now you are ready to compile this benchmark.
Have fun.